
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <!-- bootstrap -->
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <!-- jquery -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.js" integrity="sha256-eKhayi8LEQwp4NKxN+CfCh+3qOVUtJn3QNZ0TciWLP4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

        <title>공구카</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <br>
            <h3>회원가입화면입니다!</h3>
            <p>회원가입에 필요한 정보를 입력해주세요</p>

            <form action="/user/signup" method="post">
                <label class="form-label">아이디 : </label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" name="userid">
                <br>
                <label class="form-label">비밀번호 : </label>
                <input class="form-control" type="password" name="userpw">
                <br>
                <label class="form-label">유저이름 : </label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" name="username">
                <br>
                <label class="form-label">운전면허번호 : </label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" name="userlicense">
                <br>
                <label class="form-label">거주지역 : </label>
                <select class="form-select" name="residence">
                    <option value="경기도">경기도</option>
                    <option value="서울">서울</option>
                    <option value="울산">울산</option>
                    <option value="대전">대전</option>
                </select>                
                <br> 
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-warning" value="회원가입하기">
            </form>
    </body>
</html>